{"tid":1102028,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"塔利班宣稱於阿富汗擊落一架美軍B-52轟炸機","createTime":"2019-04-11T12:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T12:31:11.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96904fedd209ef9e7a331495787d7f3fe4367b93","tid":1102028,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2360/d2360461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2360%2Fd2360461.jpg&h=3a661259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲塔利班宣稱擊落美軍B-52同溫層堡壘轟炸機。（圖／示意圖／路透社）<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n駐阿富汗美軍8日才遭當地民兵組織塔利班(Taliban) 自殺炸彈攻擊，造成3名美軍死亡，對方10日再度宣稱，擊落美軍一架B-52同溫層堡壘轟炸機(B-52 Stratofortress)，並且機上所有成員全數死亡，不過此消息目前沒有獲得美國與阿富汗當局回應，暫時無法確認其真實性。<br />\n<br />\n敘利亞Muraselon新聞網10日報導，塔利班發言人宣稱，美軍一架從阿富汗赫爾曼德省(Helmand province) Shawrab空軍基地起飛的B-52戰略轟炸機，10日凌晨被位於西部希爾區(Washir)的塔利班民兵用重型武器擊落。由於擊落地點距離空軍基地不到10公里，研判很有可能起飛沒多久就被擊落。<br />\n<br />\n消息發布後至今未獲得美國與阿富汗官方回應，也沒有發布轟炸機墜毀後的相關畫面，引發外界質疑其報導真實性。陸媒《環球網》指出，對於沒有戰鬥機和先進防空武器的塔利班武裝分子來說，想要擊落B-52轟炸機的可能性十分低，再加上B-52戰略轟炸機擁有先進的自衛防禦系統，此新聞很有可能是塔利班為了造勢而放出的假消息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 美軍B-52轟炸機傳在阿富汗被擊落 塔利班：機上人員全數死亡 | ETtoday軍武 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190411/1420148.htm#ixzz5kmuqsEt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190411%2F1420148.htm%23ixzz5kmuqsEt4&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzt4xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=ce30af19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190411/1420148.htm#ixzz5kmuqsEt4</a>"},{"pid":"f05e30af24b00d25856b7d67d64655cdae67c6fe","tid":1102028,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"用咩打？？<br />\nAk47??"},{"pid":"c918592f6202a258c0b5c9f49013ae761470a8c7","tid":1102028,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c84644faa48081815f6ab3023f1b4043e064ba","tid":1102028,"uid":45821,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7uFCQOW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7uFCQOW.png&h=d9092ba4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8640306e699ecdc74ddefff8ba0d65b4336a1ff3","tid":1102028,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1eb7fb3684f91b8c3806e01e2ed309cd73c35db9","tid":1102028,"uid":79355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"打左52次飛機咋掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}